OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FDoc Martin star Martin Clunes has lost
OL,7,Fhis four-year planning battle to stop
OL,8,Fa permanent Travellers' site being
OL,9,Fbuilt on land next to his Dorset home.
OL,11,FThe actor, who also stars in the new
OL,12,FWuthering Heights film, had objected
OL,13,Fto the plans by Theo Langton and Ruth
OL,14,FMcGill along with a number of
OL,15,Fneighbours.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
