OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FThe couple, who have lived in a 45ft
OL,7,Fby 16ft (13.7m by 4.9m) mobile home on
OL,8,Fland they own at Meerhay, near
OL,9,FBeaminster, for 25 years, had applied
OL,10,Ffor planning permission to continue
OL,11,Fliving there permanently.
OL,13,FOfficers at Dorset Council had
OL,14,Frecommended the plans for approval at
OL,15,Fits western and southern area planning
OL,16,Fcommittee in April 2025, but the case
OL,17,Fwas deferred after concerns were
OL,18,Fraised about the risk of flooding at
OL,19,Fthe site.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FBut after a flood risk assessment
OL,7,Ffound that any risk of surface water
OL,8,Fflooding was not great enough during
OL,9,Fthe 100-year estimated "lifetime" of
OL,10,Fthe development, the plans went back
OL,11,Fto the committee.
OL,13,FNow the committee has voted by seven
OL,14,Fagainst two in favour of accepting the
OL,15,Fplans, along with conditions set by
OL,16,Fthe planning officers.
OL,26,@qD@XOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FThese include that the alterations to
OL,7,Fthe site can be in place only while Mr
OL,8,FLangton and Ms McGill are resident and
OL,9,Fremoved within four months of them no
OL,10,Flonger "permanently occupying" the
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FAnd the conditions would limit the
OL,14,Fnumber of residential caravans on the
OL,15,Fsite to two.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FPlanning officer Bob Burden told the
OL,7,Fcommittee that the council's gypsy
OL,8,Fliaison officer was satisfied that the
OL,9,Fcouple's movements and attendance of
OL,10,Ffestivals met the definition of
OL,11,FTravellers.
OL,13,FHe added: "There is a growing and
OL,14,Fsignificant unmet need for sites, we
OL,15,Fsimply cannot find sufficient sites
OL,16,Ffor gypsies and Travellers."
OL,26,@uD@KOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FMr Burden said the impact on
OL,7,Fneighbouring properties was limited
OL,8,Fand said: "There's no unacceptable
OL,9,Foverlooking privacy issues with this
OL,10,Fscheme in my view."
OL,12,FHe added the permission would be
OL,13,Flimited to the use of the couple and
OL,14,Fadded: "If the site ceased to be
OL,15,Foccupied then the structures would
OL,16,Fneed to be removed."
OL,26,@pD@KOUrD@SO]vD@HOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FJohn Steel KC, representing Clunes,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The applicants are not
OL,8,Fstatutory Travellers, but even
OL,9,Fassuming they are, they cannot on one
OL,10,Fhand reject sites offered to them and
OL,11,Fat the same time benefit from
OL,12,FTraveller policy exceptions."
OL,14,FHe added: "Others will follow, others
OL,15,Fare waiting, there is evidence of this
OL,16,Falready on adjacent land.
OL,18,F"The strong message will be that those
OL,19,Fwith similar lifestyles can get round
OL,20,Fthe planning system in Dorset."
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@]O]vD@KOUzD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FMr Steel continued: "To grant a
OL,7,Fpermanent planning permission would be
OL,8,Funlawful, undermine planning policy
OL,9,Fand be wholly unfair to law-abiding
OL,10,Fresidents."
OL,12,FSimon Rushton, agent for the
OL,13,Fapplicants who had lived at the site
OL,14,Ffor 21 years, said they had received
OL,15,F47 letters of support as well as the
OL,16,Flocal town council.
OL,18,FReverend Jonathan Herbert said he
OL,19,Fsupported the couple's plans and added
OL,20,Fthat they "maintained a nomadic
OL,21,Flifestyle".
OL,26,@nD@UOUrD@KO]|D@KOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FHe said: "They are well known and
OL,7,Frespected among the new Traveller
OL,8,Fcommunity, without a shadow of a doubt
OL,9,Fthey are are new Travellers."
OL,11,FCouncillor Craig Monks said: "I
OL,12,Fbelieve that the officer's
OL,13,Frecommendations provide the certainty
OL,14,Fto those local residents that this
OL,15,Fland will be used for a particular
OL,16,Fpurpose, for particular people in a
OL,17,Fparticular time."
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@]O]sD@^OUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,FClunes and his wife previously made a
OL,7,Fsubmission to the committee expressing
OL,8,Ftheir concerns over the proposals,
OL,9,Fincluding the recommendation of the
OL,10,Fcouncil's gypsy liaison officer that
OL,11,FMr Langton and Ms McGill should be
OL,12,Fconsidered as "New Age Travellers".
OL,14,FAn officer's report to the committee
OL,15,Fsaid: "It is very clear they follow
OL,16,Fand are a part of the New Age
OL,17,FTraveller community and have been for
OL,18,Fmany years.
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@bO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,F"Although they are not ethnic gypsies,
OL,7,FI am more than satisfied they are New
OL,8,FAge Travellers and have a lot of
OL,9,Ffriends and support in the new
OL,10,FTraveller community."
OL,12,FIn response, Clunes wrote: "It cannot
OL,13,Fbe concluded that the applicants are
OL,14,Fpersons of nomadic habit of life due
OL,15,Fto them visiting music and other
OL,16,Ffestivals each year to sell items and
OL,17,Fhelp set them up.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@UO]tD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772216417
OL,3,CDoc Martin star loses battle against
OL,4,CTravellers' site
OL,6,F"This would mean that many, if not
OL,7,Fall, stallholders at such festivals,
OL,8,Fas well as the roadies who travel with
OL,9,Fthe festival organisers, retailers and
OL,10,Fbands would be classed as gypsies and
OL,11,FTravellers within the planning
OL,12,Fdefinition, which clearly is not the
OL,13,Fcase."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
